CWMCM0025E.unsupported.output.explanation=Poskytovan\u00fd typ n\u00e1vratov\u00e9 hodnoty n\u00e1stroje MCP nen\u00ed podporov\u00e1n.
CWMCM0025E.unsupported.output.useraction=Zadejte n\u00e1vratov\u00fd typ, kter\u00fd je objektem.

# Used as exception message
# {0} = The name of the tool
CWMCM0026E.duplicate.tool.name=CWMCM0026E: N\u00e1stroj MCP s n\u00e1zvem {0} ji\u017e existuje.
CWMCM0026E.duplicate.tool.name.explanation=Ka\u017ed\u00fd n\u00e1stroj mus\u00ed m\u00edt jedine\u010dn\u00fd n\u00e1zev. Nelze zaregistrovat nov\u00fd n\u00e1stroj, kter\u00fd m\u00e1 stejn\u00fd n\u00e1zev jako ji\u017e existuj\u00edc\u00ed n\u00e1stroj.
CWMCM0026E.duplicate.tool.name.useraction=Zadejte jedine\u010dn\u00fd n\u00e1zev pro ka\u017ed\u00fd n\u00e1stroj MCP.

# Used as exception message
