# {0} = The name of the tool
CWMCM0027E.provide.one.handler=CWMCM0027E: Pro n\u00e1stroj MCP {0} je nutn\u00e9 zavolat bu\u010f metodu setHandler, nebo metodu setAsyncHandler.
CWMCM0027E.provide.one.handler.explanation=P\u0159i registraci nov\u00e9ho n\u00e1stroje pomoc\u00ed metody ` ToolManager, ` mus\u00edte zadat bu\u010f synchronn\u00ed obslu\u017enou funkci vol\u00e1n\u00edm metody ` setHandler `, nebo asynchronn\u00ed obslu\u017enou funkci vol\u00e1n\u00edm metody ` setAsyncHandler `. Neposkytujte oboj\u00ed.
CWMCM0027E.provide.one.handler.useraction=P\u0159i registraci n\u00e1stroje pomoc\u00ed slu\u017eby ToolManager zavolejte metodu ToolDefinition.setHandler nebo metodu ToolDefinition.setAsyncHandler.

