CWMCM0028E.invalid.character.tool.name=CWMCM0028E: {0} N\u00e1zev n\u00e1stroje MCP nen\u00ed platn\u00fd. N\u00e1zvy n\u00e1stroj\u016f mohou obsahovat pouze znaky ASCII, \u010d\u00edslice, podtr\u017e\u00edtka nebo poml\u010dky.
CWMCM0028E.invalid.character.tool.name.explanation=N\u00e1zev n\u00e1stroje nen\u00ed v souladu se specifikac\u00ed MCP pro n\u00e1zvy. N\u00e1zvy mohou obsahovat pouze znaky ASCII, \u010d\u00edslice, podtr\u017e\u00edtka, poml\u010dky a \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 jin\u00e9 speci\u00e1ln\u00ed znaky.
